  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Telomeric repeats were searched across the chromosomes using CoGeBLAST 88.",
    "To assess the phasing of both subgenomes from C. arabica, synonymous nucleotide substition (K s) values were obtained from CoGe 89 and compared between C. arabica and each of two diploid outgroups, C. canephora and C. eugenioides, using scripts in R.",
    "A reference genetic map was constructed from a cross between a Congolese group genotype (BP409) and a Congolese × Guinean hybrid parent (Q121).",
    "The segregating population was composed of 93 F1 individuals 90.",
    "The parents were sequenced to 60× and progeny to 20× coverage using the Illumina HiSeq2000 platform at Nestlé Research."
  ],
